This paper is primarily focused on optimizing imperative programs in a relational database, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the transformation of User Defined Functions (UDFs) into relational algebraic expressions, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The optimization techniques used in the paper involve cost-based optimization, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CR).
